                "exp_event_cave_goblinTrapHole_result_2": "$names$ accidentally triggered the net trap but reacted quickly enough to dodge",
                "exp_event_cave_goblinTrapHole_result_3": "$names$ fell into a pit lined with spikes\nAlthough they escaped quickly before the enemies arrived, everyone suffered some injuries",
